INSTALL
-------

1) Add the following to $CATALINA_HOME/conf/server.xml:

<Context path="/gridsphere" docBase="gridsphere" debug="0"
                 reloadable="false" crossContext="true">
     <Logger className="org.apache.catalina.logger.FileLogger"
                 prefix="localhost_gridsphere_log." suffix=".txt"
                 timestamp="true"/>
</Context>

2) Edit $CATALINA_HOME/conf/tomcat-users.xml and make sure you have the following line:


<user username="tomcat" password="tomcat" roles="tomcat,manager"/>
